These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, dutch, nigerian, italian
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, turtle, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the indian##1
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
4. the italian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the italian is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
7. the dutch is somewhere between the indian and the owner of the chinchilla##7
8. the dutch and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9
9. the nigerian and the owner of the goldfish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indian | dutch | nigerian     | italian |
| Pet           | turtle   | rabbit     | chinchilla | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, juice, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, board-games, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is card-games and the person drinking lemonade have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | water     | juice    | sprite | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | gardening | photography | board-games      | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, lemonade, 7up
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, watermelon, orange, carrot
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
2. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
8. the person drinking sprite and the person eating watermelon have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | sprite    | lemonade   | juice    | 7up  |
| Food       | watermelon | carrot | cranberry | orange |

