.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, videographer, musician, pilot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, classical, ambient, folk
1. the fan house is the videographer##1
2. the fan classical is on the right of the fan ambient##1
3. the fan classical is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
4. the fan folk is on the left or right of the musician##3
5. the fan classical is on the left of the project-manager##1
6. the pilot and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
7. the musician is on the left or right of the project-manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | pilot | musician | project-manager  | videographer |
| Music-Genre   | ambient             | classical          | folk | house    |

