.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, trance, gospel, house
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, goat, hamster
1. the fan gospel is not the owner of the goat##6
2. the owner of the chinchilla and the fan pop have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the goldfish and the fan trance have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the fan house##1
6. the fan trance is not the owner of the goldfish##6
7. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan trance##5
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan pop##1
9. the owner of the hamster is not the fan house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop | gospel | house  | trance |
| Pet           | goldfish   | chinchilla     | goat | hamster      |

