2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the fan classical is not to the right of the fan disco##8
6. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan disco##5
7. the fan classical is somewhere to the right of the fan gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | r&b | classical         | disco     |
| Sport         | rugby | surfing  | water-polo | snowboarding |

