.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, mango, eggplant, shiprot
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, van, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
2. the person eating shiprot and the person driving the airplane have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
5. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the airplane##7
6. the person eating shiprot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | eggplant | nectarine   | mango | shiprot |
| Transport   | van   | motorbike | ship    | airplane      |

