2. the mexican is not to the right of the german##8
3. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the american##3
6. the mexican is on the far left##1
7. the german is on the left of the person eating peas##1
8. the person eating kiwi is the argentine##1
9. the person eating eggplant and the german have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
