.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, soy-milk, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, sports, horror
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person drinking cola##6
2. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching sports movies and the person drinking soy-milk have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | coffee  | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | sports | horror | martial-arts      |

