.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, house, reggae
 1. the person drinking tea and the fan house have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 3. the fan gospel is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking juice##7
 4. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan house is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking coffee and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
 9. the fan reggae is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the fan gospel##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
