.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, drawing, camping, collecting
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is drawing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is drawing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | almond-milk        | iced-tea   | tea      |
| Hobby      | collecting | camping | drawing | traveling |

 